- `[SYSTEM_PROMPT]` markers → MISTRAL_V7
- `[AVAILABLE_TOOLS]` + `" [INST]"` (with quotes) → MISTRAL_V3_TEKKEN
- `[AVAILABLE_TOOLS]` + ` [INST]` (with leading space) → MISTRAL_V1
- `[AVAILABLE_TOOLS]` (without space variants) → MISTRAL_V3
- Template name starts with "mistral" or contains `[INST]` → Check above conditions

